---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Card from '../Card.astro';
---
<div class="value-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="services" class="value-section">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label">// 02 WHAT WE BUILD</p>

  <!-- Intro headline -->
  <h2 class="value-headline">
    <span>One diagnosis. Three things built for your business.</span>
    <span>One person accountable from start to finish.</span>
  </h2>

  <!-- Subhead -->
  <div class="value-subhead">
    <p>// The diagnostic tells us which one you need.</p>
    <p>// Sometimes it's all three.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Service cards bento grid -->
  <div class="services-grid">
    <!-- Card 01 - WEBSITES -->
    <Card glow>
      <p class="card-label">// WEBSITES</p>
      <h3 class="card-headline">Your website should be closing deals while you sleep.</h3>
      <p class="card-body">We build custom marketing websites that tell your business's story clearly and move visitors toward a decision. Not a template dressed up as custom work. Not a site with a new logo slapped on a stock layout. A site engineered to convert, built from a clear message, and handed off with code you own completely.</p>
      <p class="card-stat">&gt; 67% of businesses lose revenue to poor website performance.</p>
      <p class="card-timeline">// Simple sites ship in under one week.</p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Card 02 - APPS + SOFTWARE -->
    <Card glow>
      <p class="card-label">// APPS + SOFTWARE</p>
      <h3 class="card-headline">Your team should use tools built for how they actually work.</h3>
      <p class="card-body">Custom business apps for the workflows that off-the-shelf software never quite covers: intake portals, client dashboards, booking systems, internal tools, operations apps. Built around your actual process. Documented. Owned by you at delivery. Not rented from us by the month.</p>
      <p class="card-stat">&gt; 53% of small businesses report data problems from disconnected tools.</p>
      <p class="card-timeline">// App projects start at 2 weeks.</p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Card 03 - AI TOOLS -->
    <Card glow>
      <p class="card-label">// AI TOOLS</p>
      <h3 class="card-headline">Your AI should know your business, not just the internet.</h3>
      <p class="card-body">We don't bolt a chatbot onto your site and call it AI. We diagnose where AI actually saves your team time: answering FAQs, capturing leads, drafting follow-up emails, processing intake. Then we build a narrow, focused system trained on your data. No vaporware. No black boxes. A specific tool built around what your business actually does.</p>
      <p class="card-stat">&gt; Small businesses using AI save 5.6 hrs per person, per week.</p>
      <p class="card-timeline">// You see exactly what it does and why.</p>
    </Card>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .value-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.15);
  }

  /* Section label - monospace, small, amber at 35% */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.35);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Headline - Geist Pixel, two lines */
  .value-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: var(--step-4);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .value-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .value-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .value-headline span:last-child {
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.7);
  }

  /* Subhead - terminal comments, mono, amber 60% */
  .value-subhead {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .value-subhead p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--1);
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Services bento grid - 3 cols desktop, 1 col mobile */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Card internals */
  .card-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .card-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.90 0.16 62 / 0.8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .card-stat {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.7);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .card-timeline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .value-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
